{"tid":625004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特首稱康文署正檢討是否將「黃牛」活動成為刑事行為 正試驗門票實名制","createTime":"2018-04-11T05:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T16:59:59.000Z","uid":188,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dd6adaa7dbd28fa55981379dbaef026cdebd7575","tid":625004,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:49:59.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示，炒賣門票的現象近期引起關注，康文署會檢討《公眾娛樂場所條例》是否能夠適用於政府場地，令「黃牛」活動成為刑事行為，同時亦會考慮提高罰則。 林鄭月娥在立法會行政長官質詢時間表示，現時要求康文署場地租用者最少要有20%門票作公開發售，即是<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最多有80%可作內部認購</span></span>，是應表演機構的要求，因為有些表演得到商業贊助，要有一定靈活性。 她又說，康文署正試驗門票實名制，當局會留意成效，亦要視乎主辦單位是否願意合作。"},{"pid":"febdeed89159939437e932bc2c8fa1957621f1f4","tid":625004,"uid":188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:50:10.000Z","msg":"仲有20%可以買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7584767986c5d4fdabc0a7837a26b19797b8ac","tid":625004,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19be6e80559002fa95e28c7591b8e94165d0c80","tid":625004,"uid":1221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:59:56.000Z","msg":"唔係黃子華出聲屌 政府肯做野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a289e982cbcfb0dc7e073931c60e56fe52aaea","tid":625004,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:09:24.000Z","msg":"特首推實名制 除左內部飛<br />\n街外飛 入場對身份證<br />\n不得轉讓"},{"pid":"e7e2beb8e3b262d0a03880dcbdeb50b06113d1ee","tid":625004,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:13:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3708be7bdf382c696cb85df5de0d80bdd778f9fc","tid":625004,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:15:03.000Z","msg":"炒內部<img src=\"